{"tid":280530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金管局研推P2P快速支付　港元或人幣可即時跨行轉賬","createTime":"2017-06-12T07:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T07:03:40.000Z","uid":118647,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f6da83880618c16b97deedfe37b5ad988bcf8a92","tid":280530,"uid":118647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:00:50.000Z","msg":"現時不少本地銀行已先後推出個人對個人（P2P）流動支付服務，例如銀通成員網絡的「JETCO Pay」及滙豐的「PayMe」等，但始終仍未成氣候。《信報》引述市場消息指，金管局「快速支付系統」（Faster Payment）有望於明年9月最快推出，應用範圍涵蓋個人及公司客戶，並可即時進行港元或人民幣跨行轉賬過數。<br />\n<br />\n金管局發言人稱，「快速支付系統」可支持港元及多種貨幣，但首階段將支持港元和人民幣結算，而且銀行及儲值支付工具營運商均可參與，例如八達通亦可加入，用戶可將八達通資金轉至銀行戶口，有指該系統可於每周7日、每日24小時運作，即是用戶任何時間進行跨行轉賬，對方能即時收款。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/634902/xlarge/42b3ef5fea4f6e8f30203333d0dd5d5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F634902%2Fxlarge%2F42b3ef5fea4f6e8f30203333d0dd5d5f.jpg&h=8e32d41e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/97289/%E9%87%91%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80%E7%A0%94%E6%8E%A8P2P%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98-%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83%E6%88%96%E4%BA%BA%E5%B9%A3%E5%8F%AF%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E8%B7%A8%E8%A1%8C%E8%BD%89%E8%B3%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%2F97289%2F%25E9%2587%2591%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%25B1%2580%25E7%25A0%2594%25E6%258E%25A8P2P%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E9%2580%259F%25E6%2594%25AF%25E4%25BB%2598-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%2588%2596%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B9%25A3%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E8%25B7%25A8%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%25BD%2589%25E8%25B3%25AC&d=R6ovdL9rzY5bByH2AfPvFtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=065032c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/97289/%E9%87%91%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80%E7%A0%94%E6%8E%A8P2P%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98-%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83%E6%88%96%E4%BA%BA%E5%B9%A3%E5%8F%AF%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E8%B7%A8%E8%A1%8C%E8%BD%89%E8%B3%AC</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾年前就應該做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4565dd037160bc44a60bdd19dbad3cd154a2a284","tid":280530,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:03:10.000Z","msg":"加快都係明年九月，班友返工平時做d咩"},{"pid":"c9dc51683db86371b72596089e04e326e1ba491f","tid":280530,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:03:40.000Z","msg":"payme用信用卡+有積分贏晒啦其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}